{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>市面上有不少 Markdown 的编辑器，比如<a href=\"https://github.com/wizardforcel/markdown-simple-world/blob/master/1.md\">这些</a>。这些编辑器各有千秋，而大多支持 PDF 导出的都是收费软件。其中，颜值与功能并存的就是我最钟爱的就是 Atom 。Atom 漂亮的 UI 无需多言，而且它还有免费的插件支持 PDF 导出。</p>\n<h1>来来吃菜吃菜</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>language-markdown<br>markdown 语法扩展</li>\n<li>linter-markdown<br>语法检查</li>\n<li>markdown-preview-plus<br>如名所说</li>\n<li>markown-scroll-sync<br>预览栏同步滚动插件</li>\n<li>markdown-themeable-pdf || markdown-pdf <br>PDF 转化插件</li>\n<li>pdf-view<br>atom 里面查看 PDF</li>\n<li>tool-bar-markdown-writer<br>Markdown 工具栏</li>\n<li>markdown-table-format<br>表格格式化工具</li>\n<li>Markdown-Writer<br>一系列增强功能，可同步静态博客，如：jekyll，hexo</li>\n<li>markdown-img-paste<br>直接使用<code class=\"language-text\">ctrl+v</code>粘贴图片</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>不要客气</h1>\n<h3>linter-markdown</h3>\n<p>linter-markdown 需要预先安装<code class=\"language-text\">linter</code>基础插件。</p>\n<h3>PDF 转换</h3>\n<p><strong>这个插件要求 Node 环境。</strong></p>\n<p>可能有报错：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>AssertionError: html-pdf: Failed to load PhantomJS module. You have to set the path to the PhantomJS binary using 'options.phantomPath'</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>打开命令行在<strong>当前家目录</strong>下执行</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-sh line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-sh\">npm install phantomjs-prebuilt</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>如果被墙了<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/dream_an/article/details/51800523\">可以参考这里</a></p>\n<h3>工具栏</h3>\n<p>这个插件依赖于<code class=\"language-text\">tool-bar-main</code>，需要预先安装。</p>\n<h1>来来再添一碗饭</h1>\n<p>安装之前应该保证有 node 环境，和 VC++。<a href=\"https://github.com/atom/atom/blob/1.18-releases/docs/build-instructions/windows.md\">参考</a></p>\n<h1>效果预览</h1>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/98ac4/atom-markdown.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 36.23824451410658%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"atom markdown\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/10273/atom-markdown.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/9b14a/atom-markdown.png 163w,\n/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/94962/atom-markdown.png 325w,\n/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/10273/atom-markdown.png 650w,\n/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/2fc6f/atom-markdown.png 975w,\n/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/a8a2c/atom-markdown.png 1300w,\n/static/eba4f1661bd84f09a59e25f4018d72cb/98ac4/atom-markdown.png 1595w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kompasim/atom-plugins\">这里有更多有趣的插件。</a> <a href=\"http://baidu.com\">客服热线</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Markdown 编辑器"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/atom下Markdown写作指南","pre":"/post/atom-插件推荐-实用","next":"/post/nodeJS 发送带参的 POST 请求","tags":["wabpack","eslint","javascript","axios","api","react","babel","algorihm","linix","app","git","gogs","nginx","proxy","ruby","language","php","shell","cpp","language-feature","c","recursion","java","jsp","mysql","atom","markdown","nodejs","error"]}}